Did you also replace all your interface cards in your PC's.
You will not run N unless all your equipment is N. The N routers are designed to run N best.
They will run G and B also but that does not mean they do as good a job as router designed for those.
One of the main differences is the antenna layout.
First plug directly into the router with a lan cable and see if it runs faster.
You can also place your PC as close as possible to your router running on the wireless and see if it runs faster.
